WEBVTT

00:10:28.228 --> 00:10:32.236
(Music)

00:10:33.071 --> 00:10:35.340
When you've had to deal
with an asshole at work,

00:10:35.364 --> 00:10:36.539
what have you done?

00:10:36.563 --> 00:10:39.763
If you don't have the power
to get rid of them, what should you do?

00:10:40.390 --> 00:10:43.847
Sometimes, you just have to learn
how to have a hard conversation.

00:10:43.871 --> 00:10:45.029
Sheila Heen: Yeah.

00:10:45.053 --> 00:10:47.117
AG: You're a lawyer
by training, aren't you?

00:10:47.141 --> 00:10:49.817
SH: (Laughs) Do you mean
am I an asshole by training?

00:10:49.841 --> 00:10:52.512
Yes, yes I am. (Laughs)

00:10:52.536 --> 00:10:54.397
AG: Sheila Heen is a recovering lawyer

00:10:54.421 --> 00:10:57.126
who teaches negotiation
at Harvard Law School.

00:10:57.150 --> 00:11:00.516
She cofounded a company
that specializes in conflict mediation